Debrief.Wrappers

Class FixWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • MWC.GUI.PlainWrapper
      • Debrief.Wrappers.FixWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Plottable>, ColoredWatchable, Watchable, CanPlotFaded, CanvasType.MultiLineTooltipProvider, CreateEditorForParent, Editable, Exportable, Plottable, Renamable, SupportsPropertyListeners, TimeStampedDataItem
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FixWrapper.InterpolatedFixWrapper

    public class FixWrapper
extends PlainWrapper
implements Watchable, CanvasType.MultiLineTooltipProvider, TimeStampedDataItem, CreateEditorForParent, CanPlotFaded
    The fix wrapper has the responsibility for the GUI and data aspects of the fix, tying the two together.
